{
  "stem": "18397.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 398.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have no-- no-- no towel, we didn't have no soap.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have no hot water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't have no cold water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who was the-- the-- the guy you-- you-- you [INAUDIBLE] in the book?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And who was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Who was that guy?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He [SOB].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to build the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You will see [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who built the-- built the bunkers?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who built them?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I became a-- a building technician.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You'll see what are [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I build them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they're still standing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People went back and were in the-- when we were in the partisans, they say, so who's standing here that you want to see?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They say, the bunker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to take-- to take them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was doing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody else was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I was the-- the commandeers who were there, you know, with Partisans, what rather than all the garbage-- and over me was a guy who was there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he wasn't from the party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They You know, from the party, the-- the Communist party.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they couldn't make me for use for the-- for the guy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he became the guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I spoke to him a couple of months ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said-- at least, he says, when--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Brought back at least 300 people. 300 people that were our responsibility.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says to me, so he said, at least we-- we did this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we wouldn't be there, they wouldn't be-- they wouldn't survive. 300 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last-- the last thing it was, what I did, we had to blow up the-- the tracks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- had over-- over 100 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
